track.name: Frank's Wild Years
comments: One night Frank was on his way home from work, stopped at the liquor store, picked up a couple Mickey's Big Mouths- drank 'em in the car on his way to the Shell station- he got a gallon of gas in a can, drove home, doused everything in the house, torched it, parked across the street, laughing, watching it burn, all Halloween orange and chimney red...then Frank put on a top forty station got on the Hollywood Freeway headed north... Never could stand that dog...

Never could stand that dog.[3]
